metadata.description:
CryptoKevin Punks are a collection of Kevins transformed into Punks including a very special and limited selection of aliens, apes and zombies. Collection includes never before-seen combinations of traits. All CryptoKevin Punks reside on the Ethereum blockchain. 

 This collection is not affiliated with Pixelmon or Larva Labs
metadata.name: CryptoKevin Punk #1
